Top Five;;64;;86;;R;;Though he began in stand-up comedy, Andre Allen (Chris Rock) hit the big-time as the star of a trilogy of action-comedies about a talking bear. Andre is forced to spend the day with Chelsea (Rosario Dawson) a profile writer for the New York Times, whose film critic has just panned Andre's passion project about the Haitian Revolution. Unexpectedly, Andre opens up to Chelsea, and as they wind their way across New York, Andre tries to get back in touch with his comedic roots.;;Comedy;;Chris Rock;;2014;;Chris Rock,Rosario Dawson,Kevin Hart,Gabrielle Union,Tracy Morgan,Cedric the Entertainer,J.B. Smoove,Sherri Shepherd,Anders Holm,Romany Malco,Leslie Jones,Michael Che,Jay Pharoah;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/top_five